items.name: Meeting Room A
items.description: A spacious, well-equipped meeting room perfect for business meetings, workshops, and small events. Includes projector, whiteboard, and seating for up to 20 people.

items.name: Yoga Studio
items.description: A serene environment ideal for yoga classes and meditation sessions, featuring full-length mirrors, yoga mats, and a peaceful ambiance.

items.name: Private Counseling Room
items.description: A private and comfortable room designed for one-on-one consultations or counseling sessions, ensuring privacy and confidentiality.

items.name: Conference Hall
items.description: Our largest space, suitable for conferences, large workshops, and seminars. Equipped with stage, sound system, and flexible seating arrangements.

items.name: Photography Studio
items.description: A fully equipped photography studio with various backdrops, lighting equipment, and accessories. Ideal for photoshoots and small-scale video productions.
